Description: UNIQUE -- No more than 1 enhancement of this type may be slotted by a character.  Gives this power a chance to reduce the target's defense by 22.5% and reduces recharge time by {Boost.Attrib.Recharge.Scale}%.  This effect will trigger roughly 4.5 times per minute.  This enhancement can only be slotted by Brutes and may be slotted into any Brute damage power.
DisplayName: Superior Attuned Superior Unrelenting Fury F
